                        Kaufmann</rs>
               <lb xml:id="uuid_c9a2ff92-c50c-4614-a1fc-9396f8608679"/>/ <rs type="law" ref="https://alex.onb.ac.at/cgi-content/alex?aid=bgb&amp;datum=1922&amp;page=485&amp;size=45">§ 30 Pr. G.</rs> /<lb xml:id="uuid_195cae77-8cb7-424f-a9c8-aeefc5733c3b"/>expediert am 27. April 1926. </note>
         </p>
